<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="22May1924"><font color="red">22 May 1924</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Valery Larbaud): All my books and MSS are packed up (Anna Livia with them) so I cannot find what I promised. It is impossible to work any longer in this hotel. However, I send you a short poem &mdash; the first I have written in six years ((A Prayer)) </div>
